    </div>
    <div class="text-side">
      <h3>Therapy Services</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Physical therapy</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>To restore physical function, prevent falls, etc.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Occupational therapy</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>To restore activities of daily living.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Speech-language pathology</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>To restore communication problems, speech disorders.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Therapy Services must be:</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>Intended to restore function, improve mobility, or maintain your current condition</li>
            <li>Ordered by your Physician</li>
            <li>Safe and effective for your condition</li>
            <li>Complex enough to require a licensed therapist</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


