    </div>
    <div class="text-side">
      <h3>Advance Beneficiary Notice of Noncoverage (ABN)</h3>
      <p>You’ll receive an ABN when:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Service is not considered medically necessary</li>
        <li>Care is non-skilled (like bathing only)</li>
        <li>You aren’t homebound or don’t need intermittent skilled care</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


  <!-- HHCCN -->
 <section class="homehealth-section light-gray reverse">
